              "kind": "cited theorem"
            },
            {
              "source": "LPT0 constant-precision log-width",
              "target": "LPT0 constant-precision sufficient-volume width D",
              "reason": "At constant precision, D*b=Omega(log N) forces D=Omega(log N); the log-width construction embeds by zero padding unused coordinates.",
              "anchor": "Definitions 2.1-2.3 plus residual-coordinate monotonicity",
              "kind": "derived embedding"
